			<p>
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">You all might know the quest, but not know the end. I don't either, but hopefully someone who reads this does :).  Go to the bard by the docks in south q (the one you give the reports to).  Ask him about his girlfriend and he'll give you a song.  Go to the blue house near the temple of life.  It says to sing it to aenia when her dad is gone but hes always there.  If you hand either of them the song all they do is thank you.  I tryed singing it as a bard but that doesnt work either.  Hopefully theres an end.
