				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				I have done this quest a few times. Everything above is correct.<BR>
The only thing that may throw some off is to try to wait for the father to leave. You can do this quest while he is in the house with her.<BR>
Also, she tells you that Behroe works at night. Recently, I think he has changed his schedule with Anehan. They seem to be working 3 days on..three days off. All hours.<BR>
I waited for him to spawn and Anehan remained the watchman for 3 days straight without a break, and then Behroe did the same thing.<BR>
It's also a good idea to do the Watchman's Report Quest with the Bard's Guild since you will be delivering the report request to Behroe or Anehan as well.
				</font>
